                            <comment id="17429523" author="gurwls223" created="Sat, 16 Oct 2021 05:18:48 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Just for other people who face this issue from Spark 3.2.0: workaround for this issue is to set &lt;tt&gt;PYSPARK_PIN_THREAD&lt;/tt&gt; environment variable to &lt;tt&gt;false&lt;/tt&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
